Colton Ford https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Colton_Ford 0 Colton Ford (born October 12, 1962) is the stage name of the former American gay pornographic actor Glenn Soukesian, who returned to his original career path of singer and actor. As of May 2007, he resides in New York City.
